# Fitbit2Garmin crontab (for Docker container)
# Runs the Fitbit-to-Garmin sync every hour
#
# For system cron (outside Docker), use install_cron.sh instead:
#   ./install_cron.sh [--frequency "0 * * * *"]
#
# Paths are Docker-specific (/app = WORKDIR in Dockerfile).
# System cron will use paths relative to the project directory.

0 * * * * cd /app && python main.py >> /app/data/cron.log 2>&1
